data.description: PRICE REDUCED!!Seller Motivated!Welcome to this 3 bedroom 1 bath Largo home, located close to shops,schools and the sunny Florida beaches, this home has new tile  flooring and updated kitchen with new cabinets,new countertop  and new chrome appliances,the roof was replaced about 10 years ago and most of the windows were replaced with impact windows,the updated  bathroom is conveniently located adjacent to two of the bedrooms which have terrazzo floors  and the third bedroom is converted from a portion of the garage with laundry room attached.other recent updates include, hot water heater and new AC Ductwork.There is a screened porch overlooking the large fenced  backyard with a huge shed for extra storage.Don't miss this opportunity to own a home in a fantastic location and a NON-FLOOD ZONE. Seller will give $5000 credit towards buyer buying down interest rate!!
